NEAR CITY INVESTMENT PROPERTY

- Freestanding building
- Fully leased to international tenant
- $267,527 pa net rent
- Outstanding near city location
- Substantial depreciation benefits
- 1,170sqm building
- Sensational off-street parking

For further information please contact Tony Pagano 0408 721 665 or John Slater 0420 312 951.

CBRE on behalf of our valued client are pleased to present to the market 9&10/34 Campbell Street, Bowen Hills.   

Lots 9 & 10 are being offered to the market in one line and with vacant possession, providing the ideal opportunity for an owner occupier / tenant to secure this quality asset.  

The subject property offers 384sqm of high quality ground floor commercial accommodation which was fully refurbished in 2015. The current layout provides a mixture of open plan work space, partitioned offices, board/meeting rooms, staff break out area and amenities including a shower facility. 

In addition to the office, there is also an adjoining 116sqm warehouse which can be used for storage or as extra car parking on top of the 7 exclusive use bays.

Key features;

• 384sqm high quality office space
• 116sqm warehouse with roller door access
• Suitable to a multitude of users – office/retail/showroom
• Great signage to passing traffic
• 7 exclusive car bays on site
•	300m from Bowen Hills Train Station
•	Direct access to Airport Link Tunnel system

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact Exclusive Agents CBRE.

•	2 exclusive car bays + visitor parking on site
•	Boutique complex with only 4 units in total
•	Recently painted exterior and new roof installed
•	Solar power system in place providing low running costs
•	Ideal purchase for owner occupiers

The subject property is located within a small mixed use strata complex comprising of just 4 units. Taylor Street is ideally located off Sandgate Road, a major thoroughfare connecting Bowen Hills to the Brisbane CBD and major arterials. 

Bowen Hills is considered a high demand suburb after being earmarked and rezoned by EDQ as a ‘High Priority Development Area’.

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact Exclusive Agents CBRE
